le #KathleenHarrison|author=Talking Pictures TV|date= 2016-06-21|accessdate=12 February 2019|archive-url=http://archive.today/nyNld|archive-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n*''[[The L-Shaped Room]]'' (1962 drama starring [[Leslie Caron]] and [[Tom Bell (actor)|Tom Bell]])<ref>{{cite tweet|user=TalkingPicsTV|number=1074396250970173440|title=22:10 THE 'L' SHAPED ROOM (1962) drama #LeslieCaron #AnthonyBooth #BrockPeters #PatriciaPhoenix  Jane, a pregnant French girl moves into a seedy boarding house...|author=Talking Pictures TV|date=2018-12-16|accessdate=12 February 2019 |archive-date=2020-04-02|archive-url=http://archive.today/bMM9e}}</ref>\n{{col-2}}\n*''Lena's Holiday'' (1990 comedy, starring [[Felicity Waterman]])\n*''[[The Life and Death of Colonel Blimp]]'' (1943 drama, starring [[Roger Livesey]] and [[Deborah Kerr]])<ref name=\"Screen Daly\"/><ref>{{cite tweet|user=TalkingPicsTV |number=886692042574888961|title=00:00 THE LIFE AND DEATH OF COLONEL BLIMP (1943) Pressburger & Powell classic war drama #RogerLivesey #RolandCulver #DeborahKerr|author=Talking Pictures TV|date=|accessdate=12 February 2019|archive-date=2020-04-02|archive-url=http://archive.today/cPr9V}}</ref>\n*''Little Devils'' (1993 horror, starring [[Russ Tamblyn]])\n*''Malibu Beach'' (1978 comedy, starring [[Kim Lankford]])\n*''[[The Man in the Mirror (1936 film)|The Man in the Mirror]]'' (1936 comedy, starring [[Edward Everett Horton]])\n*''[[Marilyn (1953 film)|Marilyn]]'' (1953 film noir, starring [[Sandra Dorne]])<ref>{{cite tweet|user=TalkingPicsTV|number=881761996290568196|title=09:30 MARILYN (1953) crime drama #MaxwellReed #SandraDorne #LeslieDwyer A murder, an affair and a cover-up!|author=Talking Pictures TV|date=2017-07-03|accessdate=12 February 2019|archive-date=2020-04-02|archive-url=http://archive.today/w5ee5}}</ref>\n*''[[Mark of the Phoenix]]'' (1958 drama, starring [[Julia Arnall]])<ref>{{cite tweet|user=TalkingPicsTV|number=902848623016366080|title=14:00 MARK OF THE PHOENIX (1957) crime dra