avelled Thread'' (ITV 1979\u20131980)\n*''[[The Rivals of Sherlock Holmes (TV series)|The Rivals of Sherlock Holmes]]'' (ITV 1971-1973)<ref>{{cite tweet|user=talkingpicstv|number=1145376741470420992|title=THE RIVALS OF SHERLOCK HOLMES (1971) another case at 9pm #TPTV|date=30 June 2019|access-date=18 July 2019|author=Talking Pictures TV|archive-date=2020-04-02 |archive-url=http://archive.today/O6QXn}}</ref>\n*''[[Robin's Nest]]'' (ITV 1977-1981)\n{{col-break}}\n*''[[The Rogues (TV series)|The Rogues]]'' (NBC 1964\u20131965)<ref name=\"TPTV March 5 2018 schedule\"/> <ref>{{cite tweet|user=TalkingPicsTV|number=958262116657631232|title=From the beginning! The series about two related families of conmen! A joy with David Niven, Charles Boyer, Gig Young... THE ROGUES 9:25am|author=Talking Pictures TV|date=30 January 2018|accessdate=11 February 2019|archive-date=2020-04-02 |archive-url=http://archive.today/P9vX4}}</ref>\n*''Rooms'' (ITV 1975-77)<ref>{{cite tweet|user=talkingpicstv|author=Talking Pictures TV|number=1142379318280167426|title=ROOMS starts Thursday 11 July at 2pm|date=22 June 2019|access-date=23 June 2019|archive-date=2020-04-02 |archive-url=http://archive.today/ryQzp}}</ref>\n*''[[Rumpole of the Bailey]]'' (ITV 1978-1992)\n*''Scarf Jack'' (ITV 1981)\n*''[[Scotland Yard (film series)|Scotland Yard]]'' (ABC 1953-1961)<ref name=\"TPTV March 5 2018 schedule\"/><ref>{{cite tweet|user=TalkingPicsTV|number=909845733699997696|title=21:25 SCOTLAND YARD: THE CASE OF THE RIVER MORGUE (1956) #HughMoxey #GordonNeedham Police in are called investigate a dead body is stolen.|author=Talking Pictures TV|date=18 Sep 2017|accessdate=11 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190916121012/https:/twitter.com/TalkingPicsTV/status/909845733699997696|archive-date=16 September 2019}}</ref>\n*''[[Shadows (TV series)|Shadows]]'' (ITV 1975-78)<ref>{{cite tweet|user=TalkingPicsTV|author=Talking Pictures TV|title=70s children's series SHADOWS (1975-78) begins Monday 3 June